Gurucul

== GOAL

Use machine learning algorithms to recognise potential threats in cybersecurity.

== DATA

They used data obtained by IT security systems

== METHODS

Unsupervised learning.

== RESULTS

Potential threats are recognised sooner.

== ISSUES

People may have issues with their online records being monitored in such a way.

